ket, references, asset, manual playbook, prior research, external corpus, benchmark report\n+\n+## 5. Dead Ends\n+- Physical `interface/` path: use `design-interface/` packet instead.\n+- Benchmark value 78/100: current report says 70/100 conditional.\n+- More aesthetic preset files: conflicts with no-chooser guardrails.\n+- Paid reference lookup as mandatory: conflicts with optional fallback rule.\n+\n+## 6. Next Focus\n+Converged. Implement router fixes first, then rerun benchmark and playbook checks.\n+\n+## 7. Active Risks\n+- Current spec folder has no `spec.md`; this lineage intentionally did not seed it because write scope was restricted to this artifact directory.\n+- D1-inter and D4 remain unscored in the benchmark; follow-up must run live/advisor usefulness checks before claiming complete improvement.\n\nIndex: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/001-interface/research/lineages/gpt55fast/resource-map.md\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/001-interface/research/lineages/gpt55fast/resource-map.md\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/001-interface/research/lineages/gpt55fast/resource-map.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,47 @@\n+# Research Resource Map - gpt55fast Interface Lineage\n+\n+## READMEs\n+- `.opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/README.md` - interface packet overview, quick start, verification commands, and related documents.\n+\n+## Documents\n+- `.opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/SKILL.md` - runtime contract and router.\n+- `.opencode/skills/sk-design/SKILL.md` - design-family hub and mode