\"iteration\",\"run\":5,\"iteration\":5,\"mode\":\"research\",\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Manual testing, benchmark coverage, and verification gaps\",\"findingsCount\":4,\"newInfoRatio\":0.18,\"noveltyJustification\":\"Mostly confirmed existing hypotheses and added verification-specific actions around non-recursive playbook validation and unscored live dimensions.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"How should improvements be verified?\",\"Which manual testing gaps should become automated or benchmark-backed?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"How should improvements be verified?\",\"Which manual testing gaps should become automated or benchmark-backed?\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Claim improvement from doc edits without rerunning benchmark and playbook checks\",\"reason\":\"The current benchmark leaves D1-inter and D4 unscored, and the playbook states per-feature completeness needs a structural sweep until validation recurses.\",\"evidence\":\"file:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/014-routing-benchmark/design-interface/skill-benchmark-report.md:23\"}],\"sources\":[\"file:.opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/manual_testing_playbook/manual_testing_playbook.md:130\",\"file:.opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/manual_testing_playbook/manual_testing_playbook.md:144\",\"file:.opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/manual_testing_playbook/manual_testing_playbook.md:501\",\"file:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/014-routing-benchmark/design-interface/skill-benchmark-report.md:64\"],\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-27T04:50:00Z\",\"durationMs\":480000,\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55fast-1782532104406-wgsfs7\",\"generation\":1}\n+{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"run\":6,\"iteration\":6,\"mode\":\"research\",\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Prioritized improvement synthesis and explicit do-not list\",\"findingsCount\":7,\"newInfoRatio\":0.04,\"noveltyJustification\":\"Final pass found no materially new source classes; it consolidated priorities, dependencies, and eliminated alternatives.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"What are the prioritized improvements and do-not list?\",\"Has the loop converged?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"What are the prioritized improvements and do-not list?\",\"Has the loop converged?\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Add more aesthetic preset files as the main improvement\",\"reason\":\"The current aesthetic cue index already warns cues are critique-against only, not a chooser; additional presets risk weakening the anti-default contract.\",\"evidence\":\"file:.opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/references/aesthetics/README.md:26\"},{\"approach\":\"Bulk-import the external corpus into interface references\",\"reason\":\"The prior 009 synthesis rejected bulk import; leverage is operational gates and cards, not volume.\",\"evidence\":\"file:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/009-reference-asset-expansion/research/research.md:158\"}],\"convergenceSignals\":{\"rollingAvg\":0.1867,\"madScore\":0.2965,\"entropyCoverage\":1,\"compositeStop\":0.65},\"sources\":[\"file:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/009-reference-asset-expansion/research/research.md:68\",\"file:.opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/references/aesthetics/README.md:28\",\"file:.opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/SKILL.md:187\",\"file:.opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/SKILL.md:253\"],\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-27T04:56:00Z\",\"durationMs\":360000,\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55fast-1782532104406-wgsfs7\",\"generation\":1}\n+{\"type\":\"event\",\"event\":\"synthesis_complete\",\"mode\":\"research\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55fast-1782532104406-wgsfs7\",\"generation\":1,\"totalIterations\":6,\"answeredCount\":10,\"totalQuestions\":10,\"stopReason\":\"converged\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-27T04:58:00Z\"}\n","additions":8,"deletions":0},{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/001-interface/research/lineages/gpt55fast/deep-research-strategy.md","relativePath":".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/001-interface/research/lineages/gpt55fast/deep-research-strategy.md","type":"add","patch":"Index: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/001-interface/research/lineages/gpt55fast/deep-research-strategy.md\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/001-interface/research/lineages/gpt55fast/deep-research-strategy.md\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/001-interface/research/lineages/gpt55fast/deep-research-strategy.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,133 @@\n+# Deep Research Strategy - Interface Skill Improvement\n+\n+## 1. OVERVIEW\n+\n+### Purpose\n+\n+Investigate practical improvements to the `sk-design` interface mode, grounded in the live `design-interface` packet, prior 009 reference/asset research, the external 43-entry design corpus, manual testing playbook, and the routing benchmark.\n+\n+---\n+\n+## 2. TOPIC\n+\n+Improve the interface skill for efficiency, usefulness, UX, tooling, references, assets, and routing without weakening its anti-default design judgment.\n+\n+---\n+\n+<!-- ANCHOR:key-questions -->\n+## 3. KEY QUESTIONS (remaining)\n+- [x] What is the current interface skill surface and physical packet path?\n+- [x] Which prior expansion recommendations already landed, and which remain useful?\n+- [x] Which routing benchmark failures most constrain efficiency and usefulness?\n+- [x] Which UX/handoff gaps remain after reference expansion?\n+- [x] Which validation gaps should gate follow-up implementation?\n+<!-- /ANCHOR:key-questions -->\n+\n+---\n+\n+## 4. NON-GOALS\n+- Do not implement skill changes in this lineage.\n+- Do not modify any path outside the fan-out artifact directory.\n+- Do not add aesthetic presets or bulk-import external corpus material.\n+- Do not claim benchmark improvement without rerunning the benchmark in a follow-up implementation packet.\n+\n+---\n+\n+## 5. STOP CONDITIONS\n+- Stop when all key questions have evidence-backed answers and the final iteration adds low novelty.\n+- Stop no later than 10 iterations.\n+- Stop immediately if required evidence would require mutating outside the lineage artifact directory.\n+\n+---\n+\n+<!-- ANCHOR:answered-questions -->\n+## 6. ANSWERED QUESTIONS\n+- Current packet path is `.opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/`; the prompt's `.opencode/skills/sk-design/interface` is a mode alias, not a physical directory.\n+- The 009 high-value interface expansions mostly landed: shared register, brief-to-dials, mechanical/content gates, preflight card, real-UI loop, design-system/reference grounding, and MCP tool docs.\n+- Current benchmark report is `CONDITIONAL` at 70/100, not the prompt's stale 78/100; bottleneck is `routed-intra`, specifically ID-011 and ID-005.\n+- Highest leverage improvements are routing precision, split resource maps, explicit route-away output, redesign intake, required handoff manifest, and verification upgrades.\n+- Do-not list centers on avoiding preset expansion, paid-reference mandates, corpus bulk import, and implementation inside the research packet.\n+<!-- /ANCHOR:answered-questions -->\n+\n+---\n+\n+<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n+<!-- ANCHOR:what-worked -->\n+## 7. WHAT WORKED\n+- Current-state inventory first: prevented proposing references that already exist after 009. (iteration 1)\n+- Scenario-level benchmark reading: turned aggregate score into concrete ID-011 and ID-005 fixes. (iteration 2)\n+- D3/resource-overload analysis: identified split-grounding as a surgical efficiency fix. (iteration 3)\n+- External corpus cross-check: preserved useful redesign and visual-asset ideas without bulk import. (iteration 4)\n+- Manual playbook review: exposed verification gaps and live-mode requirements. (iteration 5)\n+<!-- /ANCHOR:what-worked -->\n+\n+---\n+\n+<!-- ANCHOR:what-failed -->\n+## 8. WHAT FAILED\n+- Treating the prompt's `interface` path literally failed; the repo uses `design-interface` as the physical packet.\n+- Treating the prompt's 78/100 benchmark value as current failed; live report evidence says 70/100 conditional.\n+- Looking for a top-level spec document in the provided spec folder failed; the folder currently contains only `research/`, and write scope forbids seeding docs outside the lineage artifact directory.\n+<!-- /ANCHOR:what-failed -->\n+\n+---\n+\n+<!-- ANCHOR:exhausted-approaches -->\n+## 9. EXHAUSTED APPROACHES (do not retry)\n+\n+### Bulk reference expansion -- BLOCKED (iteration 6, 2 attempts)\n+- What was tried: Compare 009 matrix and current packet inventory.\n+- Why blocked: Most high-value interface references/assets already landed; adding more bulk would reduce efficiency and risk preset behavior.\n+- Do NOT retry: Do not propose wholesale external corpus import or more aesthetic-preset files as the lead improvement.\n+\n+### Prompt benchmark value as truth -- BLOCKED (iteration 2, 1 attempt)\n+- What was tried: Search and read benchmark report artifacts.\n+- Why blocked: Current report says 70/100, conditional.\n+- Do NOT retry: Do not cite 78/100 unless a newer report artifact proves it.\n+<!-- /ANCHOR:exhausted-approaches -->\n+\n+---\n+\n+<!-- ANCHOR:ruled-out-directions -->\n+## 10. RULED OUT DIRECTIONS\n+- Treat `.opencode/skills/sk-design/interface` as a physical path: ruled out by `mode-registry.json` and filesystem evidence. (iteration 1)\n+- Optimize aggregate benchmark score without scenario diagnosis: ruled out because report names routed-intra and two failing scenarios. (iteration 2)\n+- Remove references broadly to improve D3: ruled out because discovery/connectivity are strong; overload is localized. (iteration 3)\n+- Require Mobbin/Refero for every design task: ruled out because lookup is optional, paid, and non-blocking. (iteration 4)\n+- Claim improvement from docs without benchmark/playbook verification: ruled out by unscored D1-inter/D4 and playbook validator limits. (iteration 5)\n+- Add more aesthetic preset files or bulk-import external corpus: ruled out by anti-chooser guardrails and 009 negative knowledge. (iteration 6)\n+<!-- /ANCHOR:ruled-out-directions -->\n+\n+---\n+\n+<!-- ANCHOR:carried-forward-open-questions -->\n+## 11A. CARRIED-FORWARD OPEN QUESTIONS\n+- Should redesign intake be a new small `references/design-process/redesign_intake.md` or folded into `real_ui_loop.md`? Recommendation: new small reference only if router can load it narrowly on redesign terms.\n+- Should benchmark fixtures be updated to expect `brief_to_dials.md` for ID-011, or should `MECHANICAL_PREFLIGHT` load it directly? Recommendation: do both only if a rerun confirms recall improves without unacceptable D3 cost.\n+<!-- /ANCHOR:carried-forward-open-questions -->\n+\n+---\n+\n+<!-- ANCHOR:next-focus -->\n+## 11. NEXT FOCUS\n+Converged. Follow-up implementation should start with router fixes for ID-005 and ID-011, then rerun the design-interface benchmark and playbook structural checks.\n+<!-- /ANCHOR:next-focus -->\n+\n+---\n+\n+<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n+## 12. KNOWN CONTEXT\n+- `resource-map.md` was not present in the provided spec folder; skipping spec-level coverage gate.\n+- The provided spec folder currently has only `research/`; this lineage did not create or mutate `spec.md` because the operator constrained writes to the lineage artifact directory.\n+- The routing benchmark report exists at `014-routing-benchmark/design-interface/skill-benchmark-report.md` and currently reports aggregate 70/100, conditional.\n+- Prior 009 research is high-signal but partly superseded by landed interface references/assets.\n+\n+---\n+\n+## 13. RESEARCH BOUNDARIES\n+- Max iterations: 10\n+- Convergence threshold: 0.05\n+- Completed iterations: 6\n+- Stop reason: converged\n+- Artifact root override was bound directly; `resolveArtifactRoot` was not run.\n+- Writes were limited to `.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/001-interface/research/lineages/gpt55fast`.\n","additions":133,"deletions":0},{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/001-interface/research/lineages/gpt55fast/deep-research-findings-registry.json","relativePath":".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/001-interface/research/lineages/gpt55fast/deep-research-findings-registry.json","type":"add","patch":"Index: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/001-interface/research/lineages/gpt55fast/deep-research-findings-registry.json\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/001-interface/research/lineages/gpt55fast/deep-research-findings-registry.json\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/001-interface/research/lineages/gpt55fast/deep-research-findings-registry.json\n@@ -0,0 +1,101 @@\n+{\n+  \"sessionId\": \"fanout-gpt55fast-1782532104406-wgsfs7\",\n+  \"loopType\": \"research\",\n+  \"status\": \"complete\",\n+  \"openQuestions\": [\n+    {\n+      \"id\": \"oq-redesign-placement\",\n+      \"question\": \"Should redesign intake be standalone or folded into real_ui_loop.md?\",\n+      \"recommendedResolution\": \"Standalone only if the router loads it narrowly for redesign prompts; otherwise fold into real_ui_loop.md to avoid D3 overload.\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"id\": \"oq-preflight-benchmark-expectation\",\n+      \"question\": \"Should benchmark fixtures expect brief_to_dials.md for ID-011?\",\n+      \"recommendedResolution\": \"Add brief_to_dials.md to MECHANICAL_PREFLIGHT and rerun benchmark; keep only if ID-011 improves without excessive D3 regression.\"\n+    }\n+  ],\n+  \"resolvedQuestions\": [\n+    {\n+      \"id\": \"rq-path\",\n+      \"question\": \"What is the current interface skill path?\",\n+      \"answer\": \"The hub mode is interface, but the physical packet is .opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/.\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"id\": \"rq-benchmark\",\n+      \"question\": \"What benchmark score should research ground in?\",\n+      \"answer\": \"The current report artifact says aggregate 70/100 conditional; the prompt's 78/100 appears stale or from a different run.\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"id\": \"rq-priority\",\n+      \"question\": \"What is highest leverage?\",\n+      \"answer\": \"Fix routing precision and route-away behavior before adding new references.\"\n+    }\n+  ],\n+  \"keyFindings\": [\n+    {\n+      \"id\": \"f1-current-packet-mature\",\n+      \"title\": \"Current interface packet is already reference-rich after 009\",\n+      \"priority\": \"context\",\n+      \"sources\": [\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/SKILL.md:73\", \".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/009-reference-asset-expansion/research/research.md:55\"]\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"id\": \"f2-router-bottleneck\",\n+      \"title\": \"Benchmark bottleneck is intra-router behavior, not missing connectivity\",\n+      \"priority\": \"P0\",\n+      \"sources\": [\".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/014-routing-benchmark/design-interface/skill-benchmark-report.md:17\", \".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/014-routing-benchmark/design-interface/skill-benchmark-report.md:21\"]\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"id\": \"f3-route-away\",\n+      \"title\": \"Pure logic prompt needs an explicit sk-code route-away outcome\",\n+      \"priority\": \"P0\",\n+      \"sources\": [\".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/014-routing-benchmark/design-interface/skill-benchmark-report.json:590\", \".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/SKILL.md:36\"]\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"id\": \"f4-grounding-overload\",\n+      \"title\": \"Grounding branch should split design-system grounding from Mobbin/Refero references\",\n+      \"priority\": \"P1\",\n+      \"sources\": [\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/SKILL.md:119\", \".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/014-routing-benchmark/design-interface/skill-benchmark-report.json:421\"]\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"id\": \"f5-preflight-recall\",\n+      \"title\": \"Preflight routing should include dial context and the card as a first-class asset\",\n+      \"priority\": \"P1\",\n+      \"sources\": [\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/assets/interface_preflight_card.md:16\", \".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/014-routing-benchmark/design-interface/skill-benchmark-report.json:280\"]\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"id\": \"f6-redesign-intake\",\n+      \"title\": \"Redesign work needs a preserve/overhaul intake before visual changes\",\n+      \"priority\": \"P1\",\n+      \"sources\": [\".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/external/taste-skill.md:783\", \".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/external/taste-skill.md:804\"]\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"id\": \"f7-verification\",\n+      \"title\": \"Follow-up changes need benchmark and playbook structural verification\",\n+      \"priority\": \"P1\",\n+      \"sources\": [\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/manual_testing_playbook/manual_testing_playbook.md:501\", \".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/014-routing-benchmark/design-interface/skill-benchmark-report.md:64\"]\n+    }\n+  ],\n+  \"ruledOutDirections\": [\n+    \"More aesthetic preset files as the primary improvement\",\n+    \"Bulk-importing the external corpus\",\n+    \"Requiring Mobbin/Refero lookups for every design task\",\n+    \"Mixing implementation ownership into interface rather than handing to sk-code\",\n+    \"Trusting stale prompt benchmark values over report artifacts\"\n+  ],\n+  \"metrics\": {\n+    \"iterationsCompleted\": 6,\n+    \"openQuestions\": 2,\n+    \"resolvedQuestions\": 3,\n+    \"keyFindings\": 7,\n+    \"convergenceScore\": 0.65,\n+    \"coverageBySources\": {\n+      \"skill\": 8,\n+      \"references\": 11,\n+      \"assets\": 2,\n+      \"manualPlaybook\": 5,\n+      \"priorResearch\": 4,\n+      \"externalCorpus\": 6,\n+      \"benchmark\": 10\n+    }\n+  }\n+}\n","additions":101,"deletions":0},{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/001-interface/research/lineages/gpt55fast/deep-research-dashboard.md","relativePath":".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/001-interface/research/lineages/gpt55fast/deep-research-dashboard.md","type":"add","patch":"Index: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/001-interface/research/lineages/gpt55fast/deep-research-dashboard.md\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/001-interface/research/lineages/gpt55fast/deep-research-dashboard.md\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/001-interface/research/lineages/gpt55fast/deep-research-dashboard.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,52 @@\n+# Deep Research Dashboard - Session Overview\n+\n+## 1. Status\n+- Topic: Improve sk-design interface skill efficiency, usefulness, UX, tooling, references, assets, and routing.\n+- Started: 2026-06-27T04:10:00Z\n+- Status: COMPLETE\n+- Iteration: 6 of 10\n+- Session ID: fanout-gpt55fast-1782532104406-wgsfs7\n+- Lifecycle Mode: new\n+- Generation: 1\n+- Stop reason: converged\n+\n+## 2. Progress\n+\n+| # | Focus | Track | Ratio | Findings | Status |\n+|---|---|---|---:|---:|---|\n+| 1 | Current interface packet inventory and post-009 landed state | inventory | 1.00 | 5 | complete |\n+| 2 | Routing benchmark bottlenecks and score discrepancy | routing | 0.72 | 6 | complete |\n+| 3 | Efficiency improvements in router resource loading | efficiency | 0.55 | 5 | complete |\n+| 4 | Usefulness, UX, and handoff gaps | usefulness | 0.34 | 5 | complete |\n+| 5 | Manual testing, benchmark coverage, and verification gaps | verification | 0.18 | 4 | complete |\n+| 6 | Prioritized improvement synthesis and explicit do-not list | synthesis | 0.04 | 7 | complete |\n+\n+- iterationsCompleted: 6\n+- keyFindings: 7\n+- openQuestions: 2\n+- resolvedQuestions: 3\n+\n+## 3. Questions\n+- Answered: 10/10 considered questions\n+- Remaining: 0 blocking research questions\n+- Carried forward: 2 implementation placement decisions\n+\n+## 4. Trend\n+- Last 3 ratios: 0.34 -> 0.18 -> 0.04 (declining)\n+- Stuck count: 0\n+- Guard violations: none\n+- convergenceScore: 0.65\n+- Source diversity: skill packet, references, asset, manual playbook, prior research, external corpus, benchmark report\n+\n+## 5. Dead Ends\n+- Physical `interface/` path: use `design-interface/` packet instead.\n+- Benchmark value 78/100: current report says 70/100 conditional.\n+- More aesthetic preset files: conflicts with no-chooser guardrails.\n+- Paid reference lookup as mandatory: conflicts with optional fallback rule.\n+\n+## 6. Next Focus\n+Converged. Implement router fixes first, then rerun benchmark and playbook checks.\n+\n+## 7. Active Risks\n+- Current spec folder has no `spec.md`; this lineage intentionally did not seed it because write scope was restricted to this artifact directory.\n+- D1-inter and D4 remain unscored in the benchmark; follow-up must run live/advisor usefulness checks before claiming complete improvement.\n","additions":52,"deletions":0},{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/001-interface/research/lineages/gpt55fast/resource-map.md","relativePath":".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/001-interface/research/lineages/gpt55fast/resource-map.md","type":"add","patch":"Index: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/001-interface/research/lineages/gpt55fast/resource-map.md\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/001-interface/research/lineages/gpt55fast/resource-map.md\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/001-interface/research/lineages/gpt55fast/resource-map.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,47 @@\n+# Research Resource Map - gpt55fast Interface Lineage\n+\n+## READMEs\n+- `.opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/README.md` - interface packet overview, quick start, verification commands, and related documents.\n+\n+## Documents\n+- `.opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/SKILL.md` - runtime contract and router.\n+- `.opencode/skills/sk-design/SKILL.md` - design-family hub and mode routing.\n+- `.opencode/skills/sk-design/shared/register.md` - shared Brand-vs-Product register.\n+- `.opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/references/design-process/design_principles.md` - core aesthetic process.\n+- `.opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/references/design-process/brief_to_dials.md` - Design Read intake.\n+- `.opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/references/design-process/mechanical_defaults.md` - layout gate.\n+- `.opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/references/design-process/copy_and_mock_data.md` - content gate.\n+- `.opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/references/design-process/real_ui_loop.md` - ground/reuse/render/check/handoff loop.\n+- `.opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/references/design-process/ux_quality_reference.md` - objective quality floor.\n+- `.opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/references/design-grounding/design_inventory.md` - live design-system grounding.\n+- `.opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/references/design-grounding/design_references_mcp.md` - Mobbin/Refero critique-against discipline.\n+- `.opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/references/mcp-tooling/mobbin_tools.md` - Mobbin Code Mode tool catalog.\n+- `.opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/references/mcp-tooling/refero_tools.md` - Refero Code Mode tool catalog.\n+- `.opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/references/aesthetics/README.md` - aesthetic cue guardrails.\n+\n+## Commands\n+- `.opencode/commands/deep/research.md` and `.opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep_research_auto.yaml` - loaded for loop contract only; not executed as a mutating command because the operator prebound the artifact directory and write scope.\n+\n+## Agents\n+- No sub-agents were dispatched by this leaf lineage.\n+\n+## Skills\n+- `deep-research` - loop contract.\n+- `sk-design` / `design-interface` - research subject.\n+\n+## Specs\n+- `.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/009-reference-asset-expansion/research/research.md` - prior corpus expansion matrix.\n+- `.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/014-routing-benchmark/design-interface/skill-benchmark-report.md` - benchmark summary.\n+- `.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/014-routing-benchmark/design-interface/skill-benchmark-report.json` - scenario details.\n+\n+## Scripts\n+- No scripts were run except directory creation inside the artifact directory.\n+\n+## Tests\n+- `.opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/manual_testing_playbook/manual_testing_playbook.md` - 14-scenario manual validation contract.\n+\n+## Config\n+- `.opencode/skills/sk-design/mode-registry.json` - mode-to-packet routing.\n+\n+## Meta\n+- `.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/external/` - 43-entry external corpus; sampled `taste-skill.md`, `gpt-tasteskill.md`, `redesign-skill.md`, and `impeccable.md` for interface-relevant evidence.\n","additions":47,"deletions":0}],"diagnostics":{},"truncated":false},"title":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/001-interface/research/lineages/gpt55fast/deep-research-config.json\nA .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/001-interface/research/lineages/gpt55fast/deep-research-state.jsonl\nA .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/001-interface/research/lineages/gpt55fast/deep-research-strategy.md\nA .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/001-interface/research/lineages/gpt55fast/deep-research-findings-registry.json\nA .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/001-interface/research/lineages/gpt55fast/deep-research-dashboard.md\nA .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/001-interface/research/lineages/gpt55fast/resource-map.md","time":{"start":1782532911046,"end":1782532911055}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_05d310a89fff4730016a3f49f8b8588191a51f52a0c51ed5f0"}},"id":"prt_f0738f3e9001FRFux2QUBAgpyD","sessionID":"ses_0f8ce9c7affeFPHv9jEwltlvKr","messageID":"msg_f07376547001PfWDdy8T0xWExN"}}
{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1782532911455,"sessionID":"ses_0f8ce9c7affeFPHv9jEwltlvKr","part":{"id":"prt_f073db15d001PDhdeirWRGbasv","reason":"tool-calls","snapshot":"8980ddb476e777bcfdbbec1a7bdd9a12f63dbdb2","messageID":"msg_f07376547001PfWDdy8T0xWExN","sessionID":"ses_0f8ce9c7affeFPHv9jEwltlvKr","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":209514,"input":1644,"output":8710,"reasoning":2552,"cache":{"write":0,"read":196608}},"cost":0}}
